Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts, one \Nburning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning about Caesar's motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are on the move to save the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kidnap Caesar, and escape from the island--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all while trying to escape Shinokuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have treated him\N as my young brother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and watched closely\N over him as he grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard for you, Vergo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I need you to take care of Law there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna make him wish\N that he was never born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So kill him in a horrific way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Dies from Exposure?!\N The Spine-chilling Snow Woman Monet!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:54.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}D BUILDING - THE "SAD" MANUFACTURING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like my hand has been bitten
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by my own dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even for a mischievous child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were too smart\N for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tend to die young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be easiest for me to kill \Nyou by crushing your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll torment you slowly as I please
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and warp your smart-ass face...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:46.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}C BUILDING 4TH FLOOR - CAESAR'S RESEARCH ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What does she want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bird woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go after the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing again! But it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these walls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bird woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-layer Kamakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are ten layers to this Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to break the snow walls
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they're layered one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you trying to buy time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can break them all quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can break this Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, stop wasting my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm gonna lose you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I will win\N if I fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the strongest isn't always\N the winner in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a block of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't push me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're now in my embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your power is diminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will lose all of\N your physical strength
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to my cold body in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your heart will freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,die in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing heavily around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel very tired, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the beginning\N of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What tremendous hidden strength he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But falling through here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will land him in the slide to the \Ngarbage dump deep underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll never be able to come \Nback up unless he can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect him to\N sabotage himself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:43.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}B BUILDING 3RD FLOOR - NEAR THE BISCUIT ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must never\N eat that candy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:12:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard\N but you have to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go to the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in our way,\N you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop them without hurting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect of the Rumble Ball\N is about to wear off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can eat the candy soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! To the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can eat the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take more of the drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will ruin your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save them\N because I have no power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Chopper-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with those kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've gotten more violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us what's going on, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar is trying to turn them into giants
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make them demonic \Nsoldiers, just as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle them alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have to stop them\N as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Biscuit Room is to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candies are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha is the only child in her \Nright mind and she's helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were trying to stop the other children
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is protecting the candies\N in the room all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here at the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward while I hold them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna be\N stopped so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll stop at nothing\N when they're in that state!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's evil candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We asked Chopper-chan and\N the others to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't listen to them,\N we can't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! That's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna eat it all yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let them have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home with everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit is sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to\N worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Monet-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the bird woman\N that I told you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet-san, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha, it's not nice\N to keep it all to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to share\N the candies with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she uses sorcery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Logia-type?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's our enemy, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet-san, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}B BUILDING 2ND FLOOR - AN EXAMINATION ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where did the boy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He entered into the "secret room"\N where no one is allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and transformed into a small dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy named Momonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brat who transformed into a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, "the boy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know\N about that, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching it secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened in the "secret room"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got here on the same ship \Nwith him so I've been worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This laboratory is big and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are various treatment rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's just in a different room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he eating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he eat anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, he's eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone about him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the "secret room." Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe one of the\N children knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to let the Master know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:19:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd come to this secret room myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the only place I can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all their fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could've been a great show - \Neverything perfect and lovely,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and more befitting of the\N world's greatest scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they screwed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy G-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them regret ruining my plan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after they go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow down to my scientific prowess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys frustrated because your \Nscheme is coming crashing down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is that important to you guys, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, you squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me, my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "What a shame."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty sure that I could \Ntake my heart back from Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't expect you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vergo-san to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have to be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to silence\N you anyway, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so pleasant to watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a scumbag like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.57,0:23:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate -
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker's rage explodes at the fact \Nthat Vergo's betrayed his men,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Vergo closes in on him \Nwith overwhelming Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fierce battle between Smoker and Vergo intensifies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as Smoker puts his spirit and \Npride as a Marine on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fists Collide!\N A Battle of the Two Vice Admirals!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.46,0:23:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
